post_text:
Our summer feeding program starts today with grab-and-go meals available from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. Today's menu includes cheeseburgers, beef dippers and barbecue chicken sandwiches. Meals are available in the car rider lines at 5 schools - Table Rock Middle School 1585 NC 126;
Mountain View Elementary School 805 Bouchelle St.;
Valdese Elementary School 298 Praley St. NW;
East Burke Middle School 3519 Miller Bridge Road; and
George Hildebrand Elementary 8078 George Hildebrand School Road. And the following mobile bus sites:
11 a.m. - Hillcrest Elementary - 201 Tennessee St.;
11:45 a.m. PPG Paint Store - 511 Burkemont Ave.; and
12:30 p.m. Walker Road Baptist Church - 100 Walker Road.
Meals will be served at these sites on Tuesdays and Fridays.
Visit bit.ly/BCPSGrabLunch or call 828-433-8047 with questions or comments.

